WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:23.160
This is your senator, Estes Keifoffer, who is one of the busiest legislators in Washington.

00:23.160 --> 00:27.360
He has constantly engaged in legislative activity which benefits the people of the great state

00:27.360 --> 00:32.200
of Tennessee as well as all Americans. Despite his busy schedule, Senator Keifoffer

00:32.200 --> 00:36.240
looks forward to being with his wife and children in the evening when they have an opportunity

00:36.240 --> 00:41.080
to discuss their normal family activities. Senator Keifoffer has received why to claim

00:41.080 --> 00:45.240
for his work in the crime investigations and to trust hearings and the present investigations

00:45.240 --> 00:49.740
into the drug industry. He is also vitally concerned with matters of great local interests

00:49.740 --> 00:54.520
such as TBA, the Reclamation Projects Farm Legislation, the high cost of living and

00:54.520 --> 00:59.240
numerous other problems that affect your everyday life. Senator Keifoffer has served

00:59.240 --> 01:06.000
in Congress since 1939 and has been in the Senate for 12 years. As your personal representative

01:06.000 --> 01:11.440
and friend, the senator would like to meet you. So let's join the family in their Washington

01:11.440 --> 01:16.080
home. Senator Keifoffer.

01:16.080 --> 01:20.920
My friends, I certainly would like to be with you and personal on this occasion, but of

01:20.920 --> 01:25.980
course I have a lot of places to be in Tennessee. I do hope that during the summer I can have

01:25.980 --> 01:32.520
an opportunity of visiting with you personally and talking with as many of you as possible.

01:32.520 --> 01:39.460
But on this occasion I do want you to meet again my family, my wife Nancy whom all of

01:39.460 --> 01:44.240
you know and Nancy you want to say something to the...

01:44.240 --> 01:49.360
Yes, I'm glad to be with you too. I actually want to get down to Tennessee as much as I

01:49.360 --> 01:53.720
can the summer and be with you in the next few months.

01:53.720 --> 01:59.800
And then our oldest daughter cannot be with us on this occasion because she's struggling

01:59.800 --> 02:05.120
hard to try to get by her freshman year at Vanderbilt, but Nancy I think you got a picture

02:05.120 --> 02:07.640
of Linda. You didn't see that when it just came the

02:07.640 --> 02:13.200
mail the other day. Well I'm anxious to see it and I know that Linda will be with us this

02:13.200 --> 02:19.320
summer a great deal too. And here's my great big boy David. David Estes Keifoffer. David

02:19.320 --> 02:26.320
how are you getting along? Far from at school we just had a fair and I want to cat it.

02:26.320 --> 02:31.440
Oh school, that's fair. Well that may have to get out. That may have two cats we had.

02:31.440 --> 02:35.800
Why'd you do that little bit of kitten? Well I had to give it away because we already

