had two dogs in one cat. You mean you drew a number in one little kitten? Yes.

02:41.760 --> 02:46.280
I used a cute little kitten I saw him but I saw to agree with you that one around the

02:46.280 --> 02:54.280
house maybe enough. And Diane, this is our daughter Diane. She's not 12 years old and

02:54.280 --> 02:59.120
she goes to school. What are you going to do this summer Diane? Well I'm planning to go

02:59.120 --> 03:04.640
down to Tennessee after camp and help my sister around the house. Want to help Linda

03:04.640 --> 03:09.800
what her own little house on Lookout Mountain? Well I hope that we just got our house finished

03:09.800 --> 03:15.480
this last summer. We hope that as many of you as possible may come and visit us sometime

03:15.480 --> 03:22.120
when we were there. I believe you have a big job of feeding the dogs in the cat most

03:22.120 --> 03:28.440
of the time don't you Diane? Supposed to. Supposed to but and well Gail how are you getting

03:28.440 --> 03:36.480
along sweetie? Gail is nine years old and are you going to come down and travel around

03:36.480 --> 03:41.840
with us sometime this summer? Yeah well I got to camp first. And then I remember four

03:41.840 --> 03:47.680
years ago you went several places with Nancy and me when we were in our campaign and what

03:47.680 --> 03:53.880
you do in there when you went around. They're going your buttons. Put buttons on people.

03:53.880 --> 03:57.880
I remember you put a button on you try to give a fellow a button he wouldn't take one

